            <lg xml:id="TK419">
<l>nuṇaṅkiya kēḷviya rallār vaṇaṅkiya</l>
<l>vāyiṉa rātal aritu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is a rare thing to find modesty, a reverend mouth- with those who have not received choice instruction.</l>
